ssName=\"text-[12.5px] text-white/60 font-light leading-relaxed mb-6\">\n521 |                 In alignment with GFF AI's strict security protocols, the developer workspace is isolated to physical client-side sandbox simulators for demonstration accuracy.\n522 |               </p>\n523 | \n524 |               <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-4\">\n525 |                 {BOUNDARIES.map((item, idx) => (\n526 |                   <div \n527 |                     key={idx}\n528 |                     className={`p-4 rounded-xl border ${item.border} bg-gradient-to-br ${item.color} flex flex-col gap-2`}\n529 |                   >\n530 |                     <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n531 |                       <span className=\"text-[12px] font-mono font-bold text-white\">\n532 |                         {item.title}\n533 |                       </span>\n534 |                       <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-[#009DFF]/20\">\n535 |                         {item.badge}\n536 |                       </span>\n537 |                     </div>\n538 |                     <p className=\"text-[11.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light\">\n539 |                       {item.text}\n540 |                     </p>\n541 |                     <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-2 mt-1 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/45\">\n542 |                       <span className=\"text-white/20\">PROD PARADIGM:</span> {item.prod}\n543 |                     </div>\n544 |                   </div>\n545 |                 ))}\n546 |               </div>\n547 |             </div>\n548 | \n549 |             {/* Sidebar Notice 2: Reference Manual */}\n550 |             <div className=\"rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-black/40 p-6 flex flex-col gap-4\">\n551 |               <h4 className=\"text-[12px] font-mono text-white/40 font-bold uppercase track